      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "id": "cls2-meth-t",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 80,
      "y": 958,
      "width": 740,
      "height": 264,
      "text": "\n+ __init__(api_token, base_url, max_retries, default_retry_delay)\n+ list_roles(workspace_id, item_id) : tuple[list[dict], Optional[str]]\n+ put_roles(workspace_id, item_id, roles, etag) : Optional[str]\n+ put_roles_dry_run(workspace_id, item_id, roles) : bool\n- _roles_url(workspace_id, item_id) : str\n- _auth_headers() : dict\n- _get_with_retry(url) : requests.Response\n- _put_with_retry(url, headers, body) : requests.Response\n",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "cls2-meth",
      "originalText": "\n+ __init__(api_token, base_url, max_retries, default_retry_delay)\n+ list_roles(workspace_id, item_id) : tuple[list[dict], Optional[str]]\n+ put_roles(workspace_id, item_id, roles, etag) : Optional[str]\n+ put_roles_dry_run(workspace_id, item_id, roles) : bool\n- _roles_url(workspace_id, item_id) : str\n- _auth_headers() : dict\n- _get_with_retry(url) : requests.Response\n- _put_with_retry(url, headers, body) : requests.Response\n",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "baseline": 14
    },
    {
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1624805617,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 122288352,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1776715455703,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "id": "cls2-desc",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 80,
      "y": 1252,
      "width": 740,
      "height": 462,
      "text": "CLASS: OneLakeSecurityClient: REST client for the Fabric Data Access\nRoles API.\n\nMETHODS:\n+ list_roles(workspace_id, item_id): GET current data access roles and\ntheir ETag.\n\n+ put_roles(workspace_id, item_id, roles, etag): PUT the full set of\nroles (replaces all existing roles).\n\n+ put_roles_dry_run(workspace_id, item_id, roles): Validate roles\nwithout applying (dryRun=true).\n\n- _get_with_retry(url): GET with 429 retry logic.\n\n- _put_with_retry(url, headers, body): PUT with 429 retry logic (does\nNOT retry 412 \u2014 that's the caller's job).",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "CLASS: OneLakeSecurityClient: REST client for the Fabric Data Access\nRoles API.\n\nMETHODS:\n+ list_roles(workspace_id, item_id): GET current data access roles and\ntheir ETag.\n\n+ put_roles(workspace_id, item_id, roles, etag): PUT the full set of\nroles (replaces all existing roles).\n\n+ put_roles_dry_run(workspace_id, item_id, roles): Validate roles\nwithout applying (dryRun=true).\n\n- _get_with_retry(url): GET with 429 retry logic.\n\n- _put_with_retry(url, headers, body): PUT with 429 retry logic (does\nNOT retry 412 \u2014 that's the caller's job).",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "baseline": 18
    },
